{"tid":1435692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有個天水圍前線居民朋友 佢有D野講...","createTime":"2019-08-09T06:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T07:31:01.000Z","uid":266289,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7c205df5f7155200cdbc53e7e26960b7b8ada419","tid":1435692,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:17:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">代朋友po: <br />\n<br />\n我就住響最近天水圍警署嗰幾幢其中一幢<br />\n屋企個窗對到狗屋正一正 完全被迫前線<br />\n啱啱睇完醫學界嗰個記招嬲撚到仆街 <br />\n忍唔住要講 <br />\n屌你老味林鄭月娥星期三鬼鬼鼠鼠嚟到天水圍 仲去差館慰問班狗<br />\n如果俾我知道 <br />\n即刻九秒九沖落去 要求同佢對話<br />\n班攔坦用山埃過期催淚彈毒害我哋居民 <br />\n射撚到放題咁 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你唔撚係走來慰問我哋 <br />\n反而係嗰班化武施襲者</span></span><br />\n我仲交啲差餉黎做乜撚<br />\n全部用返曬嚟幫我地成幢居民買豬咀 換冷氣機啦仆街<br />\n<br />\n星期一嗰日我搭lift <br />\n然後有一個滿頭白髮嘅婆婆入lift <br />\n我問佢去邊, 出面好危險<br />\n佢唔知發生咩事 話要去買藥<br />\n我叫佢唔好行前門要行後門 前門有催淚彈<br />\n跟住佢話唔驚 啲人唔會蝦阿婆<br />\n我完全吹佢唔脹 所以唯有陪佢去買 好彩果幾分鐘無放到<br />\n根本有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多老人家小朋友都唔知發生咩事就被無辜受害</span></span> 最仆街就係班撚樣連黑旗都唔出就放 想走都走唔切 <br />\n有幾多片睇返d BB同小朋友呀食咗你哋啲山埃幾陰公幾辛苦 仲好可能有後遺症 特別係記者們<br />\n仲有果D十幾歲落街買書, 踢住對拖, 就話涉嫌非法集結, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係又拉唔係又拉, 唔係警權過大係乜撚嘢呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n幫我推撚到比特首辦公室助理睇 俾佢老細睇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭月娥 我屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後 我想響度呼籲各區特別係受催淚彈影響嘅居民X要交差餉或響應交稅嘅X合作運動, 諗一諗點解我地要出糧比呢班仆街</span></span>"},{"pid":"87479333d61f162b1a6791a4cbfc7beaaa46eb66","tid":1435692,"uid":266289,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實天水圍唔歡迎你</span></span>"},{"pid":"2af2e3df7312263ac74bfba87d346356a48ce9fa","tid":1435692,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:21:05.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"3c50d6281b95bb5b7681c18a6e79260f5e98ab83","tid":1435692,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:21:34.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"a79f93d36b9225af71221c1c3b1d1cdb35f53f0c","tid":1435692,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"42eae5e0b2f4b72c5491dc7b97cfcc31eb55209f","tid":1435692,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:23:11.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"defdafa3d89c4105b343347c4844e00272530d3c","tid":1435692,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:23:15.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"bd33f1a73e1f1b94c972ce76298624d383e56c12","tid":1435692,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"908e4f6c918d37106c53bb7104f8d292c0db80b9","tid":1435692,"uid":281418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:23:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78c02f823a23c53467263b6ce1f5075d489a611d","tid":1435692,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:25:45.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"de0a5389bd9ad0fc66fa691e9e4a1fac8bd361ba","tid":1435692,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"3ea92d0b8b39ca4f848bfec62939e4ac908d73a7","tid":1435692,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"ef2acef95b5fe37c8298440d013680f17bcdcc7a","tid":1435692,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c344dbacce25412957071d8fbc13c8233ff0d62d","tid":1435692,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:32:36.000Z","msg":"所以而家警暴係我地最有力最聚焦既進攻，建議可用呢個代替時代革命 呢個較模糊既口號。"},{"pid":"8df532dae5ac6262e05a47986b42063da7652f3c","tid":1435692,"