\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d976de48540c952b3ab1df4eba7c446c3e9ceb2b","tid":1435692,"uid":149435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:46:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要由朝放到晚呀仆街<br />\n黑警死全家！比天收啦<br />\n林奠我屌你老母呀！！<br />\n天水圍唔歡迎你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}